'''世界護照'''（World Passport）是由[[世界服務機構|世界服務機構]]（World Service Authority, WSA），一個由蓋瑞‧戴維斯於1948年成立的非營利機構<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.romingerlegal.com/tenthcircuit/10th_circuit/99-1334.htm |title=99-1334 - U.S. v. Thomas - 07/07/2000<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2010-08-15 |archive-date=2010-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100206221359/http://www.romingerlegal.com/tenthcircuit/10th_circuit/99-1334.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，援引[[世界人權宣言#第十三條|世界人權宣言第十三條第二款]]發行的證件。其被[[國際民航組織|國際民航組織]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.icao.int/Meetings/mrtd-Zimbabwe2012/Documents/2-11-Esteves_Portugal-forensic.pdf |title=International Civil Aviation Organization Regional Seminar on MRTDs, Biometrics and Border Security, 27-29 November 2012, p30 |accessdate=2019-04-18 |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104151824/https://www.icao.int/Meetings/mrtd-Zimbabwe2012/Documents/2-11-Esteves_Portugal-forensic.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.icao.int/Meetings/TAG-MRTD/Documents/Tag-Mrtd-16/TagMrtd16_005_en.pdf |title=International Civil Aviation TECHNICAL ADVISORY GROUP ON MACHINE READABLE TRAVEL DOCUMENTS, TAG-MRTD/16, WP/5, 13/9/05, section 2.1.1 |accessdate=2019-04-18 |archive-date=2017-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171110114415/https://www.icao.int/Meetings/TAG-MRTD/Documents/Tag-Mrtd-16/TagMrtd16_005_en.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[歐洲聯盟理事會|歐洲聯盟理事會]]<ref name="European Council">[http://register.consilium.europa.eu/pdf/en/08/st16/st16225.en08.pdf Table of travel documents entitling the holder to cross the external borders and which may be endorsed with a visa - (Parts II and II) and Part V (documents to which visas cannot be affixed] {{Wayback|url=http://register.consilium.europa.eu/pdf/en/08/st16/st16225.en08.pdf |date=20110719162227 }}. [[歐洲聯盟理事會|歐洲聯盟理事會]]. 1 December 2008. 見第37頁。</ref>名列為「假想文件」(fantasy documents)。

世界護照已被報告曾「事實上」逐案被150多個國家所接受（例如蓋上{{tsl|en|Passport stamp|簽證或入出境驗訖章}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldgovernment.org/visas.html?s=1|title=WSA Passport Acceptance - Visas on WSA Passports|publisher=|accessdate=2010-08-15|archive-date=2011-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512003724/http://www.worldgovernment.org/visas.html?s=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，[[布基纳法索|布基纳法索]]，[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]，[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]，[[多哥|多哥]]和[[赞比亚|赞比亚]]曾經在法律上明確地正式承認世界護照<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldgovernment.org/official.html?s=1|title=Official Letters of Recognition|publisher=|access-date=2010-08-15|archive-date=2012-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204042510/http://www.worldgovernment.org/official.html?s=1}}</ref>。然而，布基纳法索在1992年撤回了對世界護照的認可，尚比亞亦被報告撤回了認可。加拿大<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.unhcr.org/refworld/topic,4565c2252c,4565c25f39b,3ae6ace26c,0.html|title=Refworld - Nigeria: Information on the "world passport", its validity, the issuing agency/company; on whether it is recognized as a travel document by any government; and on its use by Nigerian citizens|author=United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees|work=Refworld|accessdate=2010-08-15|archive-date=2012-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121120183135/http://www.unhcr.org/refworld/topic,4565c2252c,4565c25f39b,3ae6ace26c,0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[新西兰|新西兰]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.immigration.govt.nz/opsmanual/4851.htm |title=A2.15 Unacceptable travel documents （15/12/2006） |accessdate=2010-08-15 |archive-date=2010-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100819073704/http://www.immigration.govt.nz/opsmanual/4851.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[瑞士|瑞士]]{{Citation needed|date=June 2009}}及[[美国|美国]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://foia.state.gov/masterdocs/07fam/07m1310.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-03-07 |archive-date=2008-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080307015819/http://foia.state.gov/masterdocs/07fam/07m1310.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>的移民部門亦聲明他們不認可該等證件，由於它並非由充分的政府機構發出，因此不符合護照的規定。中国政府声明不承认世界护照<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hrdonline.com/common/newsDis.SouIDC?method=soo&hrdonline=3dfce885a21f657f7306f92c5d448667&hrd=237008bc1cc4cf8b9fbdfd7efe0d6ff2&hrdtwo=46fdd22dc97c24a3260b6afeb87f7488 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-11-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201085420/http://hrdonline.com/common/newsDis.SouIDC?method=soo&hrdonline=3dfce885a21f657f7306f92c5d448667&hrd=237008bc1cc4cf8b9fbdfd7efe0d6ff2&hrdtwo=46fdd22dc97c24a3260b6afeb87f7488 |archivedate=2010-12-01 }}</ref>，但使用世界护照确曾取得过有效中国签证<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.worldgovernment.org/visas/2/China0001.jpg |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-11-21 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305115505/http://www.worldgovernment.org/visas/2/China0001.jpg }}</ref>。發出於2007年1月的最新版世界護照，是具有供電腦輸入之字符編碼條的可機讀證件（MRD），帶有雙重影像防偽照片，列印並封有塑膠膜。

